<!-- notifications/templates/emails/user-credentials.hbs -->
<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h2>Welcome to Quarry Master</h2>
    
    <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
    
    <p>Your account has been created successfully. Here are your login credentials:</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p><strong>Login Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
        <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>
        <p style="color: red;"><strong>Note:</strong> This is a one-time password that will expire in 24 hours.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p><strong>Important:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>You must change your password upon first login</li>
        <li>This temporary password will expire in 24 hours</li>
        <li>For security reasons, please do not share these credentials</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Login URL: {{loginUrl}}</p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or issues, please contact the system administrator.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>Quarry Master Team</p>
</div>